        %p Over the past few years, I have developed an increasingly intense interest in photography. Working to improve my skills, I've explored the medium and come to love shooting on film most of all. I now shoot and process my film at home, and I'm beginning to explore darkroom printing.
        %p My photography and my work as a software developer are closely related. Both help exercise different creative processes and I pay attention to what I learn. Often lessons about field can be applied to the other. You can see my work at the links below.
